				<div class="comment-body"><p>Victor:</p>
<p><em>Nobody</em> can submit their work for the Hugo Awards. There is no Committee that selects the short lists or winners. The nominations and final selections are made by the thousands of members of the World Science Fiction Society, not by a small select committee, so there&#8217;s no submission process. See our longer article about <a href="../../index.html?page_id=191" title="Submitting Your Work" rel="nofollow">Submissions</a> for a more detailed explanation.</p>
</div>

